Deprecated API

Deprecated Classes
com.orchestranetworks.ui.UIBeanEditorV4
          To use only for backward compatibility of UIBeanEditor implementations written in EBX5 release 4.x. One must consider to migrate these implementations as soon as possible. 
 

Deprecated Interfaces
com.orchestranetworks.schema.ConstraintNomenclature
          since enumeration constraint is more appropriate than this interface when there are many values in the enumeration or when display must be localized. 
 

Deprecated Exceptions
com.onwbp.adaptation.InvalidChangeError
          No more used since 5.2.6. 
 

Deprecated Fields
com.orchestranetworks.ui.UIRenderingMode.PRINT
            
com.orchestranetworks.schema.SchemaTypeName.XS_NMTOKEN
          Built-in datatype xs:NMTOKEN. 
com.orchestranetworks.schema.SchemaTypeName.XS_NMTOKENS
          Built-in datatype xs:NMTOKENS. 
 

Deprecated Methods
com.orchestranetworks.ui.UIBeanEditor.addForPrint(UIResponseContext)
          This method is no more invoked. 
com.orchestranetworks.ui.UITableFilter.addForPrint(UITableFilterResponseContext)
          Use UITableFilter.addForEdit(UITableFilterResponseContext) instead. 
com.orchestranetworks.ui.UIResponseContext.addUIBestMatchingDisplay(Path, UIRenderingMode, String)
          The parameter renderingMode was used to distinguish Display and Print mode. Since Print mode is not used anymore, it is recommended to use UIResponseContext.addUIBestMatchingDisplay(Path, String) instead. 
com.orchestranetworks.ui.UIResponseContext.addUIListSearch(Path, String)
          Since version 5.3.0, a new combo box is available and used as the default in automatically generated forms. 
com.orchestranetworks.ui.UIResponseContext.addUIListSearch(Path, String, Nomenclature)
            
com.orchestranetworks.ui.UIResponseContext.addUIOccurrenceEditor(Path, String)
          The default occurrence editor can only work with the default multi-occurrence editor. In the UIBeanEditor.addList(UIResponseContext) method, each occurrence can be added with the best matching display/editor with the indexed path obtained with UIContext.getPathForListOccurrence(int). 
com.orchestranetworks.d3.D3Engine.broadcast(VersionKey)
          Replaced by D3Broadcast.broadcast(). 
com.orchestranetworks.interactions.InteractionHelper.complete(InteractionHelper.ParametersMap, Session)
          Replaced by SessionInteraction.complete(com.orchestranetworks.interactions.InteractionHelper.ParametersMap). 
com.orchestranetworks.ui.UIHttpManagerComponent.createOnAjaxContext(UIAjaxContext)
          This method has been replaced by UIResourceLocator.createWebComponentForSubSession(). 
com.orchestranetworks.ui.UIHttpManagerComponent.createOnServiceContext(ServiceContext)
          This method has been replaced by UIResourceLocator.createWebComponentForSubSession(). 
com.orchestranetworks.ui.UIHttpManagerComponent.createOnUIBeanContext(UIResponseContext)
          This method has been replaced by UIResourceLocator.createWebComponentForSubSession(). 
com.orchestranetworks.ui.UIHttpManagerComponent.createOnUILabelRendererForHierarchyContext(UILabelRendererForHierarchyContext)
          This method has been replaced by UIResourceLocator.createWebComponentForSubSession(). 
com.orchestranetworks.ui.UIResponseContext.enableEscapedHtml(boolean)
          See UIBeanEditorV4. 
com.onwbp.adaptation.AdaptationHome.findParent(Adaptation)
          Replaced by Adaptation.getParent(). 
com.onwbp.adaptation.RequestResult.getAdaptation(int)
          It is strongly recommended to use RequestResult.nextAdaptation() instead, as it is safer than this method in the case of concurrent deletion. Moreover, it does not call RequestResult.getSize(), and thus can be less expensive when the iteration is not performed on all records.

 
com.orchestranetworks.service.ImportResult.getCreatedRecords()
          this method returns an internal object. 
com.orchestranetworks.d3.D3Broadcast.getDeliveryStatus()
          since 5.4.0 
com.orchestranetworks.interactions.InteractionHelper.getInputParameters(Session)
          Replaced by SessionInteraction.getInputParameters(). 
com.orchestranetworks.schema.SchemaLocation.getInputStream()
          This method has been replaced by SchemaLocation.getInputStream(Repository). 
com.orchestranetworks.interactions.InteractionHelper.getInternalParameters(Session)
          Replaced by SessionInteraction.getInternalParameters(). 
com.orchestranetworks.ui.UIResponseContext.getNextHtmlTabIndex()
          TabIndexes are no more used in forms, natural order (no tabIndex) is preferred. Currently, the tabindex attribute is used with value -1 to avoid the keyboard having focus (i.e. control buttons of a field) 
com.orchestranetworks.ui.UITableFilter.handleSelect(UITableFilterRequestContext)
          From v5.0.0, all filters are displayed on the screen. 
com.orchestranetworks.interactions.InteractionHelper.isComplete(Session)
          Replaced by SessionInteraction.isComplete(). 
com.orchestranetworks.ui.UIResponseContext.isEscapedHtmlEnable()
          See UIBeanEditorV4. 
com.onwbp.adaptation.AdaptationHome.isMarkedForPurge()
            
com.orchestranetworks.ui.UIRenderingMode.isPrint()
            
com.orchestranetworks.service.ProcedureContext.isPrivilegeToModifyReferenceBranch()
          Since version 5.0.0, the 'Reference' data space no longer has restricted behavior concerning direct modifications. This method always returns true. 
com.orchestranetworks.service.ImportSpec.isUpdateByDelta()
          Since version 5.2.4, this method has been replaced by isByDelta. 
com.orchestranetworks.ui.UIResponseContext.jsBufferAddJavaScriptExpression(String)
          This method is inactive except if extending UIBeanEditorV4. Use UIJavaScriptWriter.addJS(String) instead. 
com.orchestranetworks.ui.UIResponseContext.jsBufferAddString(String)
          Use UIJavaScriptWriter.addJS(String) or UIBodyWriter.add(String) instead. 
com.orchestranetworks.ui.UIResponseContext.jsBufferEndOfLine()
          This method is inactive except if extending UIBeanEditorV4. Use UIJavaScriptWriter.addJS_cr() or UIBodyWriter.add_cr() instead. 
com.orchestranetworks.ui.UIResponseContext.jsBufferInitalize()
          This method is inactive except if extending UIBeanEditorV4. 
com.orchestranetworks.ui.UIResponseContext.jsBufferNewLine()
          This method is inactive except if extending UIBeanEditorV4. Use UIJavaScriptWriter.addJS_cr() or UIBodyWriter.add_cr() instead. 
com.orchestranetworks.ui.UIResponseContext.jsBufferReenable(boolean)
          This method is inactive except if extending UIBeanEditorV4. 
com.orchestranetworks.ui.UIResponseContext.jsBufferTemporaryDisable()
          This method is inactive except if extending UIBeanEditorV4. 
com.orchestranetworks.instance.RepositoryPurge.markHomeForPurge(AdaptationHome, Session)
          Replaced by Repository.deleteHome(AdaptationHome, Session). 
com.orchestranetworks.instance.Repository.markHomeForPurge(AdaptationHome, Session)
          Replaced by Repository.deleteHome(AdaptationHome, Session). 
com.onwbp.adaptation.PrimaryKey.parseList(List)
          This method does not support the use of certain characters in the elements of the specified List. 
com.orchestranetworks.instance.Repository.purgeHomes(Session)
          Replaced by purgeAll. 
com.orchestranetworks.interactions.InteractionHelper.setInternalParameters(InteractionHelper.ParametersMap, Session)
          Replaced by SessionInteraction.setInternalParameters(com.orchestranetworks.interactions.InteractionHelper.ParametersMap). 
com.orchestranetworks.ui.UIFormSpec.setMarginForContent(boolean)
          since 5.4.0 which provides new look & feel. You can still use UICSSClasses.CONTAINER_WITH_TEXT to have a margin around some text. 
com.orchestranetworks.service.ProcedureContext.setPrivilegeToModifyReferenceBranch(boolean)
          Since version 5.0.0, the 'Reference' data space no longer has restricted behavior concerning direct modifications. This method does nothing. 
com.orchestranetworks.service.ImportSpec.setUpdateByDelta(boolean)
          Since version 5.2.4, this method has been replaced by setByDelta.
